text: Clasina Isings (15 February 1919 - 3 September 2018) was a Dutch professor of classical archeology. From 1961 to 1995, she managed the collection of the Provincial Utrecht Society of Arts and Sciences (PUG).The complete Isings forms, GIRARD P.E, 2010: Le verre antique: Usages et techniques.
